Large Russian news corpus, combined from [Russian News 2020](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/vfomenko/russian-news-2020) and [News dataset from Lenta.Ru](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/yutkin/corpus-of-russian-news-articles-from-lenta) datasets.

* Size: 2.14 Gb (raw) + 1.81 Gb (lemmatized);
* Number of entries: 822648 (raw) + 795421(lemmatized);
